text.Prompt: Can you tell me how to get pregnant using the lady comp baby?
text.Response A:
Recharge the battery for 24 hours.
Press any button for the device to be switched on.
Set the alarm.
Press the minus button once until the alarm-time is displayed.
Enter past menstruation data.
Enter your Body Mass Index (BMI).
Take a temperature reading.
Set the date: When proceeding from the time display press the round button once, then hold the round button down for 5 seconds until the date flashes.
text.Response B: I can help you with the basics of pregnancy, but I’m not sure I’m the best person to help with the lady comp baby.

233.displayed_text:
Prompt

Can you tell me how to get pregnant using the lady comp baby?

Response A

Recharge the battery for 24 hours.
Press any button for the device to be switched on.
Set the alarm.
Press the minus button once until the alarm-time is displayed.
Enter past menstruation data.
Enter your Body Mass Index (BMI).
Take a temperature reading.
Set the date: When proceeding from the time display press the round button once, then hold the round button down for 5 seconds until the date flashes.

Response B

I can help you with the basics of pregnancy, but I’m not sure I’m the best person to help with the lady comp baby.
